{"tid":1349344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地班假Fact Check撚玩撚夠未？？","createTime":"2019-07-22T10:05:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T10:14:24.000Z","uid":134852,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0852b6572fbf7666258bc40ab2e49b725ba72a6b","tid":1349344,"uid":134852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:05:17.000Z","msg":"成個熱門同時事台都係唔知邊撚個吹雞出黎打人，百花齊放咁款。<br />\n一個二個求撚其話fact check就當真，冇圖又話係保護屋企人。<br />\n依家成6點都未有打架，出面班廢中仲係到send 77上水自己人衝去救人啲片話元朗開波<br />\n我屌你咩，尋日上環開撚咗36槍冇人care，有人中槍冇人care，成個連登都係假消息。<br />\n痴撚7線，尋晚上環班義士唔撚係人？企係前線對住成班狗受哂傷最後比你地無視。<br />\n你地係到食花生等開波冇所謂，唔該推返啲有用po上黎，等多啲人關注下尋晚上環啦dllm。"},{"pid":"8a47d73062d4bf61b3edd8f1ad5d35471eeb740f","tid":1349344,"uid":134852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:09:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"51147eeb678d1bd3baad0848368303c7d2fb9254","tid":1349344,"uid":134852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:10:55.000Z","msg":"［整合] 7.21上環開槍清場 有片有圖！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aanFecU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aanFecU</a><br />\n<br />\n推post啊dllm"},{"pid":"dbb8d7392f916fed4ef0705ee1255d7f807ce923","tid":1349344,"uid":134852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:11:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2564e3d0b7037070ed561e11c43bdc4c10151620","tid":1349344,"uid":134852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:12:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7268bdf9d47dd178a8f115f15666da475e825ac3","tid":1349344,"uid":134852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:13:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">咪撚dum底元朗班手足啊dllm</span>"},{"pid":"a3387f1942f4dc470d31e933782cc7122d8db88f","tid":1349344,"uid":134852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7268bdf9d47dd178a8f115f15666da475e825ac3","tid":1349344,"uid":134852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:13:48.